data.description: Large corner lot is a feature of this charming 2 bedroom one bathroom home. Spacious living and dining area with updated kitchen. Don't let age be of concern as seller has had all necessary updates taken care of. New furnace and air conditioner, pex plumbing and the wiring has all been updated. Roof is less than 5 years old. Simply move in and make this house your new home! Convenient location in Knob Noster makes this home a definite plus! Full basement with an additional outside access. Great opportunity for someone looking for a home that is move in ready. Quick! Take a look and Make this House your new Home!
